## **Short Note (Points)**

* IEEE 802.11ah uses **star and grouped (TIM/RAW)** topologies to support thousands of IoT devices.
* Provides **WPA3-SAE, AES encryption, PMF, ACLs** for strong security.
* Long-range, low-power Wi-Fi ideal for outdoor and industrial IoT.
* Reduces collisions and energy use via RAW scheduling.
